  "prompt": "How can I change my name in Clash of Clan?",
  "response": "Changing your name in *Clash of Clans* is possible, but it comes with some restrictions. Here's how you can do it:\n\n### Steps to Change Your Name:\n1. **Open the Game**: Launch *Clash of Clans* on your device.\n2. **Go to Your Profile**: Tap on your player profile icon in the top-left corner of the screen.\n3. **Edit Name**: Click on the **Edit** button (it looks like a pencil) next to your current name.\n4. **Enter a New Name**: Type in the new name you want to use.\n5. **Confirm the Change**: Once you\u2019re happy with the new name, confirm the change.\n\n### Important Notes:\n- **One-Time Free Change**: You can change your name once for free.\n- **Cost for Additional Changes**: After the first free change, you\u2019ll need to use **Gems** to change your name again. The cost increases with each subsequent change.\n- **Name Restrictions**: Your new name must comply with *Clash of Clans* guidelines. Avoid using inappropriate language, special characters, or offensive terms.\n\nIf you\u2019ve already used your free name change and don\u2019t have enough gems, you\u2019ll need to earn or purchase gems to proceed.\n\nLet me know if you need further assistance! \ud83d\udc4d",
